    to find what your next adventure holds!</p>
  </div>

  <div class="col-12 col-sm">
    <h3>Checkout what others are playing!</h3>
    <br />
    <p>Check out what other people around
    the world are currently playing!</p>
  </div>

  <div class="col-12 col-sm">
    <h3>Want to review a game?</h3>
    <br />
    <p>Leave your thoughts on a game
    you've played for others to see!</p>
  </div>
</div>

